article_title: READY: It’s not just the first day of May
article_text:
READY: It’s not just the first day of May

Posted May 2, 2016 at 8:26 AM

Updated May 2, 2016 at 8:31 AM

article_metadata.description:
Happy Day Before May Day 2016. It’s the 121st day of the year (122nd in leap years) on the Gregorian calendar.
According to some TV and internet ads, changes are coming to Social Security on May 1 that will “threaten the financial security of millions of Americans.”
Those of us over 65 have already been “threatened” so often by rumors of Medicare being cut or being dragged under by Obamacare or being pushed over a cliff in our wheelchairs, etc. we longer jump when
